title: MUMBLE_REMOVE_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYER_BY_SERVER_ID
content:
0x930BD34B// MumbleRemoveVoiceTargetPlayerByServerId
void MUMBLE_REMOVE_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYER_BY_SERVER_ID(int targetId, int serverId);Parameters:targetId: A Mumble voice target ID, ranging from 1..30 (inclusive).serverId: The player's server id to remove from the target.Removes the specified player from the user's voice targets.Performs the opposite operation of MUMBLE_ADD_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYER_BY_SERVER_ID
